snippet.textDisplay: Off topic for this video, but in regards to blinging out your refrigerator.  They make panels that are magnetized and can be custom made for your refrigerator door (most people do this to match cabinets or some other look they're going for. ) You could have the 0anels cut and bling them offsite and then just slide them into place when done and TA DA you have your custom refrigerator door. Best part is if you want a change just remove the current panels and customize  another pair of panels to whatever and another look for the house. You'd probably have to create a storeroom just for your custom refrigerator door panels. I sure hope this made sense. Great job on the room!
